name: collider (itch) (jethrosoup)
description:
made the game in a couple days to teach myself godot.

the asteroids are gravitationally attracted to your ship. try to get the rocks to smash into each other instead of into you. go for the high score!

art assets by the incomparable kenney :) https://kenney.nl/

music: whole tone limbo - godmode [youtube audio library]
